  2x^2+3x+3\over (x+1)(x^2+1) 
 {2x^2+3x+3\over (x+1)(x^2+1) } =  { A\over x+1 } + { Bx+C\over x^2+1} 
 {2x^2+3x+3\over (x+1)(x^2+1) } =  { A(x^2+1) } + (Bx+C)(x+1) 
